{"tid":2109111,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"特斯拉美國工廠130多位工人確診新冠，曾接觸超1500人","createTime":"2020-07-15T04:04:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-15T13:32:52.000Z","uid":101328,"like":129,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":66,"replies":[{"pid":"deaab9b5a555fc8a9e854eec260761d93af546c0","tid":2109111,"uid":101328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T04:04:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n據美國福克斯網報道，特斯拉位於加州弗裏蒙特工廠的新冠確診病例激增。<br />\n<br />\n行業新聞網站Electrek援引特斯拉內部泄露的數據報道稱，目前超過130名特斯拉工人，加上12名承包商和臨時僱員，已檢測出新冠呈陽性。<br />\n<br />\n報告稱，確診的新冠病例曾接觸超過1550名員工。他們中的大多數沒有去檢測。特斯拉沒有立即迴應福克斯商業頻道的問題。<br />\n<br />\n該報告發布之前，特斯拉弗裏蒙特工廠的員工曾不顧加州政府禁止復工的指令，於5月份重返工作崗位，引發很多爭議。特斯拉CEO馬斯克曾威脅要起訴當地政府，並將特斯拉遷出該州。<br />\n<br />\n馬斯克當時在推特上寫道，「通過我們在特斯拉中國工廠的經驗，特斯拉比Alameda當地官員更瞭解需要做什麼來確保安全。」"},{"pid":"9d7ce19bd54c4d6484610bd0e31795ad6e19e92a","tid":2109111,"uid":101328,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T04:05:19.000Z","msg":"牛牛新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f46cc10b105b07fc9d7374512ba385e853dd3716","tid":2109111,"uid":201604,"like":32,"dislike":2,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T04:05:40.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">武漢肺炎</span>"},{"pid":"81c407e31b970c1a8ca2cbdd1cad19014a32b9ed","tid":2109111,"uid":191815,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T04:08:09.000Z","msg":"今晚千跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d834bebf1e00633885e12f89137ce9d19196eca5","tid":2109111,"uid":195827,"like":47,"dislike":1,"score":46,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T04:08:21.000Z","msg":"直上一萬美金啦<br />\n而家個市邊有可能睇基本面<br />\n好消息升 壞消息千升<br />\n多